WEBVTT

00:00:56.713 --> 00:01:00.868
the more I felt this hypocrisy
creeping up inside me.

00:01:02.865 --> 00:01:04.690
What if I was actually really mean?

00:01:07.877 --> 00:01:10.614
When I was 10 years old,

00:01:12.155 --> 00:01:15.175
there was a girl in my class
at school named Vicky.

00:01:15.199 --> 00:01:16.648
(Sigh)

00:01:16.672 --> 00:01:18.218
And I tormented her ...

00:01:20.330 --> 00:01:21.480
mercilessly.

00:01:23.359 --> 00:01:24.750
I mean, everyone did.

00:01:24.774 --> 00:01:26.358
Even the teachers picked on her.

00:01:27.769 --> 00:01:29.666
It doesn't make it any better, does it?